Ikka-tt-inn '''Masinisa''' iga yan ugllid [[Imaziɣen|amaziɣ]], ig agllid amzwaru n [[Numidya|tgeldit n Numidya]]. Ittyura ismn nes ɣikad ⵎⴵⵏⴵⵏ (MSNSN) s igʷʷmay alibu-maziɣ. Iga MASNSN u GYY u ZLLSN. Ilul ɣ -238 immet ɣ -148.

'''Masinisa''' iga agllid imqquran g umzruy amaziɣ . ilul g usggʷas n 238 dat n tlalit n lmasiḥ , g tgldit n masin. ikka-tt-inn iga argaz idusn. ar ittmaɣ xf tmurt nns ar tigira n tudrt nns. ittwassan s tnka n iysan d ufrag d tayri n tmazirt nns.umi yumz tanbaḍt , yufa masinissa kigan n tmnaḍin n tmazirt nns g ifassn n umddurruy n iruminiyn d iqrtajn. ɛwarin n wattas n imnɣan , ismun timnaḍin ad, ismunt ntn ɣ yat tgldit taxatart. isɣuda masinissa tudrt n ugdud nns. isbuɣla tadamsa n tgldit nns s ussimɣr n ufars n imndi d uzatim d idqqi. issugt inyalkamn imzzizayn akd tmizar yaḍn. anaruz n masinissa: tilelli d tamunt n ifriqya n yizzlmḍ. llig immut g usgg°as 148 bra n uzmz n ɛisa, iskr as agdud ns yan usmḍl imqqurn g tmnadt n yiɣrm n qsstantin. da ttinin ittwassn masinissa amzwaru s wawal nns: <<tafriqt n ifriqiyn>>

